		<title>觅真：真诚的感恩浸透著民心所向</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/9/27/n10746220.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Thu, 27 Sep 2018 16:39:42 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[自由广场]]></category>
