		<title>谢田：人们为什么特别喜欢被奉承（中）</title>
		<link>http://www.epochtimes.com/gb/18/9/24/n10736705.htm</link>
		<pubDate>Tue, 25 Sep 2018 05:52:15 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[自由广场]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[评论]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[奉承]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[修炼]]></category>
